{
  "name": "RPlog_An_Evening_s_Entertainment",
  "title": "An Evening's Entertainment",
  "summary": "Roused late at night by an unfamiliar red-haired servant named Raisa, the former favorite Ylsa Estrallas is dressed and brought before the Hutt crime lord Ullo for a gala she dreads. Ullo's cruel entertainment is revealed: a duel to the death over Ylsa between his sadistic brute Mephisto and her captured lover, the Corellian Paul Nighman, whom the besotted slave-girl Ilyana has unwittingly delivered into the Hutt's hands. After a tender farewell, Paul fights Mephisto with a Mandalorian blade and superior speed, suffering grievous wounds. Realizing Ullo's betrayal, the distraught Ilyana climbs a light fixture and shatters it, plunging the hall into darkness and electrocuting herself. In the chaos Paul kills Mephisto, gathers the dying Ilyana and the blinded Ylsa, and they flee through the secret passages beneath the palace toward a waiting speeder and escape off-world.",
